sequenceDiagram
    title Tobii Eye Tracker Screening Test Flow
    actor Guardian
    actor Child
    participant LexoraWeb as Lexora Web App
    participant TobiiApp as Tobii Service
    participant Backend as Next.js Backend
    participant S3 as AWS S3
    participant MLService as ML Service

    %% Init
    Guardian->>LexoraWeb: Start Tobii screening
    LexoraWeb-->>Guardian: Select child
    Guardian->>LexoraWeb: Select child
    LexoraWeb->>TobiiApp: Check Tobii service availability
    TobiiApp-->>LexoraWeb: Return connection status
    
    alt Tobii not connected
        LexoraWeb-->>Guardian: Show error & troubleshooting
        Guardian->>LexoraWeb: Retry connection
    end

    %% Calibration
    LexoraWeb-->>Guardian: Calibration instructions
    Guardian->>Child: Hand over to child
    LexoraWeb-->>Child: Display 5-point calibration
    Child->>LexoraWeb: Follow points
    TobiiApp-->>LexoraWeb: Report calibration quality
    
    alt Calibration failed
        LexoraWeb-->>Child: Show fail message
        Child->>LexoraWeb: Retry calibration
    end

    %% Tasks Loop (Simulated for 1, 2, 3)
    note right of Child: Task 1: Syllables
    LexoraWeb-->>Child: Display Task 1
    LexoraWeb->>TobiiApp: Start gaze streaming
    TobiiApp-->>LexoraWeb: Stream fixation data (WebSocket)
    
    alt Completion
        LexoraWeb->>LexoraWeb: Detect end OR Child clicks Done
        LexoraWeb->>TobiiApp: Pause gaze streaming
    end
    LexoraWeb->>LexoraWeb: Store Task 1 locally
    
    Guardian->>LexoraWeb: Review & Continue (Task 2 & 3 follow similar pattern)

    note right of Child: Task 2: Pseudo-words & Task 3: Meaningful Text
    %% (Abbreviated for brevity as logic duplicates Task 1)
    LexoraWeb-->>Child: Complete Tasks 2 & 3
    
    %% Data Submission
    LexoraWeb->>LexoraWeb: Combine all tasks
    LexoraWeb->>Backend: Submit all fixation data
    Backend->>S3: Upload raw data
    S3-->>Backend: Return file reference
    
    %% Prediction
    Backend->>MLService: Request prediction
    MLService->>MLService: Extract features & Run model
    MLService-->>Backend: Return result with confidence
    
    %% Result
    Backend->>Backend: Save record
    Backend-->>LexoraWeb: Return result
    LexoraWeb-->>Guardian: Display result & recommendations
